        Morbidly obese patients aged from 18 to 65.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  morbid obese patients aged from 18-65,

          -  BMI &gt; 40 kg/m2 or BMI&gt; 35 kg/m2 with severe comorbidities: diabetes, sleep apnea,
             hypertension etc.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  psychiatric illness,

          -  substance abuse,

          -  previous gastrointestinal surgery, and

          -  any patient who transfers from laparoscopic to convention procedure.
      </textblock>
